00:15:05,972 --> 00:15:07,839
     at hanging up a towel?!

308
00:15:08,974 --> 00:15:11,209
        We're just trying
        to be supportive.

309
00:15:11,311 --> 00:15:13,896
   Well, I'm tired of it! I've
      had enough of you two

310
00:15:13,980 --> 00:15:16,120
     being so proud of every
