00:15:18,485 --> 00:15:20,051
            [panting]

313
00:15:21,754 --> 00:15:23,755
    I think you should leave.

314
00:15:24,457 --> 00:15:27,926
     First of all, great job
     yelling at us, sweetie.

315
00:15:28,128 --> 00:15:33,164
  No one can make their parents
  feel more worthless than you.

