00:16:14,207 --> 00:16:15,841
and I shouldn't have
snapped at my parents.

329
00:16:16,743 --> 00:16:19,544
 But that's exactly why I didn't
   tell them I'm a Wonderbolt.

330
00:16:20,246 --> 00:16:23,448
       I don't understand;
    they're so proud of you.

331
00:16:24,150 --> 00:16:24,849
             [sigh]

332
00:16:25,151 --> 00:16:26,518
    Can I tell you something?

333
00:16:27,320 --> 00:16:27,818
              Sure.

334
00:16:28,120 --> 00:16:30,388
         OK, but you might want
         to hold onto your wings

335
00:16:30,490 --> 00:16:33,425
         because this could rock
         you to your very core.

336
00:16:34,049 --> 00:16:37,849
 ♪♪

337
00:16:38,030 --> 00:16:39,680
       Believe it or not,
        there was a time

338
00:16:39,733 --> 00:16:42,333
        when I wasn't the
       best at everything.

339
00:16:42,435 --> 00:16:43,469
             [gasp]

